https://www.tiny.cloud/docs/tinymce/6/npm-projects/

npm install tinymce@^6


put this inside the head:
<script src="/path/or/uri/to/tinymce.min.js" referrerpolicy="origin"></script>
<script>
  tinymce.init({
    selector: '#mytextarea'
  });
 </script>


attach the instacne to an element with that selector:
<body>
    <h1>TinyMCE Quick Start Guide</h1>
    <form method="post">
      <textarea id="mytextarea">Hello, World!</textarea> <-- default value
    </form>
</body>


get content:
tinymce.activeEditor.getContent()

set content:
tinymce.activeEditor.setContent('<span>some</span> html')
